# Ouroboros session-churn artifacts — regenerated every battle-test run; tracking them
# churns the git index and overwhelms the Cursor/VS Code Git extension. Keep .ouroboros/plugins/
# tracked since it contains real code.
.ouroboros/sessions/
.ouroboros/state/
.ouroboros/parse_failures/

# Ouroboros benchmark diagnostic outputs (contain API response bodies; copy to
# docs/benchmarks/artifacts/ explicitly if you want to include in a report)
.ouroboros/benchmarks/

# Git worktrees (development workspaces)
.worktrees/

# Leftover from aborted git filter-branch (safe to delete if present)
